			<description><![CDATA[<p>
	Principal Software Engineer - Foxboro, MA</p>
<p>
	The leading cloud platform and applications company for enabling connected products, is seeking a top-notch Principal Software Engineer to take on an unparalleled technical opportunity in the development of our client&rsquo;s software solutions. You will be a leader in the R&amp;D organization, collaborating with an Agile Team to define and implement technology solutions that enable the product suite and platform to meet phenomenal market and product opportunities. The successful candidate will have a track record and passion for delivering innovative high quality product solutions that delight customers.<br />
	Responsibilities/Duties:<br />
	&bull; Collaborate with cross functional Scrum team members to deliver innovative product features on a monthly basis<br />
	&bull; Deliver full lifecycle feature development - requirements analysis, design and production code implementation with accompanying unit an integration tests<br />
	&bull; Prototype and assess new technologies and product concepts<br />
	&bull; Collaborate with product owners &amp; other stakeholders on functional and non-functional requirements in order to deliver the appropriate technology solution<br />
